Transifex,is,an,open,service,allowing,people,to,collaboratively,translate,software,documentation,and,other,types,of,projects,Designed,as,a,hub,for,translations,of,open,source,projects,Transifex,supports,translations,straight,from,the,project,s,source,The,Transifex,API,is,a,RESTful,API,that,allows,developers,to,build,their,own,applications,using,Transifex,s,tools